Foto, bisa kuambilkan untukmu.

57
00:04:56,426 --> 00:04:59,315
Oh, kurasa aku bisa.

58
00:05:00,561 --> 00:05:02,623
Kupikir aku harus menawarkan.

59
00:05:08,220 --> 00:05:12,198
