155
00:15:02,510 --> 00:15:04,119
<i>Apa maksudmu?</i>

156
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:06,574
Seseorang masuk ke kamarku.

157
00:15:06,588 --> 00:15:09,042
<i>Aku nggak ngerti.</i>

158
00:15:10,039 --> 00:15:12,928
Pasporku dicuri.

159
00:15:14,522 --> 00:15:16,305
Tak apa-apa, aku mendapatkan
yang sementara.

160
00:15:16,306 --> 00:15:19,439
Itu hanya butuh waktu beberapa minggu. /
<i>Kamu ada pemotretan hari Senin.</i>

161
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:21,223
